Package com.arjuna.mw.wscf.model.twophase.status

Class Summary
Cancelled The coordinator has cancelled and completed the protocol.
Cancelling The coordinator is in the process of cancelling.
CancelOnly The status of the coordination is such that it will eventually cancel.
Confirmed The coordinator has confirmed and completed the protocol.
Confirming The coordinator is in the process of confirming the participants.
HeuristicCancel All of the coordiantor's participants cancelled when they were asked to confirm.
HeuristicConfirm All of the coordinator's participants confirmed when they were asked to cancel.
HeuristicHazard Some of the coordinator's participants cancelled, some confirmed and the status of others is indeterminate.
HeuristicMixed Some of the coordinator's participants cancelled and some confirmed.
Prepared The coordinator has prepared.
Preparing The coordinator is preparing.
